{"surahDetails":{"id":88,"arabicName":"الغاشية","banglaName":"বিহ্বলকর ঘটনা","englishName":"The Overwhelming","enTranslatedName":"Al-Ghashiyah","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":92,"totalLetters":378,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/88.mp3","totalAyah":26},"surah":{"id":88,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","bangl_text":"আপনার কাছে আচ্ছন্নকারী কেয়ামতের বৃত্তান্ত পৌঁছেছে কি","english_text":"Has there reached you the report of the Overwhelming [event]","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5968.mp3","colorText":"هَلْ أَتَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>كَ حَدِيثُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْغَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>شِيَةِ <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","bangl_text":"অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে লাঞ্ছিত","english_text":"[Some] faces, that Day, will be humbled","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5969.mp3","colorText":"وُجُو<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>هٌ ي</tajweed>َوْمَئِذٍ خَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>شِعَةٌ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","bangl_text":"ক্লিষ্ট, ক্লান্ত।","english_text":"Working [hard] and exhausted","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5970.mp3","colorText":"عَامِلَ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ةٌ ن</tajweed>َّاصِبَةٌ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","bangl_text":"তারা জ্বলন্ত আগুনে পতিত হবে।","english_text":"They will [enter to] burn in an intensely hot Fire","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5971.mp3","colorText":"تَصْلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةً <span class=end>٤</span>"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","bangl_text":"তাদেরকে ফুটন্ত নহর থেকে পান করানো হবে।","english_text":"They will be given drink from a boiling spring","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5972.mp3","colorText":"تُسْقَىٰ مِنْ عَيْنٍ ءَانِيَةٍ <span class=end>٥</span>"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","bangl_text":"কন্টকপূর্ণ ঝাড় ব্যতীত তাদের জন্যে কোন খাদ্য নেই।","english_text":"For them there will be no food except from a poisonous, thorny plant","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5973.mp3","colorText":"لَّيْسَ لَهُمْ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ض</tajweed>َر<tajweed class=madda_permissible>ِي</tajweed>عٍ <span class=end>٦</span>"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","bangl_text":"এটা তাদেরকে পুষ্ট করবে না এবং ক্ষুধায়ও উপকার করবে না।","english_text":"Which neither nourishes nor avails against hunger","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5974.mp3","colorText":"لَّا يُسْمِنُ وَلَا يُغْنِى مِ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ج</tajweed><tajweed class=madda_permissible>ُو</tajweed>عٍ <span class=end>٧</span>"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","bangl_text":"অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে, সজীব","english_text":"[Other] faces, that Day, will show pleasure","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5975.mp3","colorText":"وُجُو<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>هٌ ي</tajweed>َوْمَئِ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>ذٍ ن</tajweed>َّاعِمَةٌ <span class=end>٨</span>"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","bangl_text":"তাদের কর্মের কারণে সন্তুষ্ট।","english_text":"With their effort [they are] satisfied","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5976.mp3","colorText":"لِّسَعْيِهَا رَاضِيَةٌ <span class=end>٩</span>"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","bangl_text":"তারা থাকবে, সুউচ্চ জান্নাতে।","english_text":"In an elevated garden","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5977.mp3","colorText":"فِى جَ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َةٍ عَالِيَةٍ <span class=end>١٠</span>"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","bangl_text":"তথায় শুনবে না কোন অসার কথাবার্তা।","english_text":"Wherein they will hear no unsuitable speech","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5978.mp3","colorText":"لَّا تَسْمَعُ فِيهَا لَ<tajweed class=madda_normal>ـٰ</tajweed>غِيَةً <span class=end>١١</span>"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","bangl_text":"তথায় থাকবে প্রবাহিত ঝরণা।","english_text":"Within it is a flowing spring","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5979.mp3","colorText":"فِيهَا عَيْ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نٌ ج</tajweed>َارِيَةٌ <span class=end>١٢</span>"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","bangl_text":"তথায় থাকবে উন্নত সুসজ্জিত আসন।","english_text":"Within it are couches raised high","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5980.mp3","colorText":"فِيهَا سُرُ<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>رٌ م</tajweed>َّرْفُوعَةٌ <span class=end>١٣</span>"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","bangl_text":"এবং সংরক্ষিত পানপাত্র","english_text":"And cups put in place","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5981.mp3","colorText":"وَأَكْوَا<tajweed class=idgham_ghunnah>بٌ م</tajweed>َّوْضُوعَةٌ <span class=end>١٤</span>"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","bangl_text":"এবং সারি সারি গালিচা","english_text":"And cushions lined up","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5982.mp3","colorText":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصْفُوفَةٌ <span class=end>١٥</span>"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","bangl_text":"এবং বিস্তৃত বিছানো কার্পেট।","english_text":"And carpets spread around","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5983.mp3","colorText":"وَزَرَابِىُّ مَ<tajweed class=qalaqah>بْ</tajweed>ثُوثَةٌ <span class=end>١٦</span>"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","bangl_text":"তারা কি উষ্ট্রের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করে না যে, তা কিভাবে সৃষ্টি করা হয়েছে","english_text":"Then do they not look at the camels - how they are created","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5984.mp3","colorText":"أَفَلَا يَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نظ</tajweed>ُرُونَ إِلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْإِبِلِ كَيْفَ خُلِقَتْ <span class=end>١٧</span>"},{"id":18,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং আকাশের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করে না যে, তা কিভাবে উচ্চ করা হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the sky - how it is raised","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5985.mp3","colorText":"وَإِلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed><tajweed class=laam_shamsiyah>ل</tajweed>سَّم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َا</tajweed>ٓءِ كَيْفَ رُفِعَتْ <span class=end>١٨</span>"},{"id":19,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং পাহাড়ের দিকে যে, তা কিভাবে স্থাপন করা হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the mountains - how they are erected","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5986.mp3","colorText":"وَإِلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْجِبَالِ كَيْفَ نُصِبَتْ <span class=end>١٩</span>"},{"id":20,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং পৃথিবীর দিকে যে, তা কিভাবে সমতল বিছানো হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the earth - how it is spread out","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5987.mp3","colorText":"وَإِلَى <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَرْضِ كَيْفَ سُطِحَتْ <span class=end>٢٠</span>"},{"id":21,"arabic_text":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","bangl_text":"অতএব, আপনি উপদেশ দিন, আপনি তো কেবল একজন উপদেশদাতা","english_text":"So remind, [O Muhammad]; you are only a reminder","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5988.mp3","colorText":"فَذَكِّرْ إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َم<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> أَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>نت</tajweed>َ مُذَكِّرٌ <span class=end>٢١</span>"},{"id":22,"arabic_text":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","bangl_text":"আপনি তাদের শাসক নন","english_text":"You are not over them a controller","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5989.mp3","colorText":"لَّسْتَ عَلَيْه<tajweed class=ikhafa_shafawi>ِم ب</tajweed>ِمُصَيْطِرٍ <span class=end>٢٢</span>"},{"id":23,"arabic_text":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","bangl_text":"কিন্তু যে মুখ ফিরিয়ে নেয় ও কাফের হয়ে যায়","english_text":"However, he who turns away and disbelieves","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5990.mp3","colorText":"إِلَّا مَ<tajweed class=ikhafa>ن ت</tajweed>َوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ <span class=end>٢٣</span>"},{"id":24,"arabic_text":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","bangl_text":"আল্লাহ তাকে মহা আযাব দেবেন।","english_text":"Then Allah will punish him with the greatest punishment","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5991.mp3","colorText":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>للَّهُ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْعَذَابَ <tajweed class=ham_wasl>ٱ</tajweed>لْأَكْبَرَ <span class=end>٢٤</span>"},{"id":25,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় তাদের প্রত্যাবর্তন আমারই নিকট","english_text":"Indeed, to Us is their return","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5992.mp3","colorText":"إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ إِلَيْن<tajweed class=madda_obligatory>َآ</tajweed> إِيَابَهُمْ <span class=end>٢٥</span>"},{"id":26,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তাদের হিসাব-নিকাশ আমারই দায়িত্ব।","english_text":"Then indeed, upon Us is their account","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5993.mp3","colorText":"ثُ<tajweed class=ghunnah>مّ</tajweed>َ إِ<tajweed class=ghunnah>نّ</tajweed>َ عَلَيْنَا حِسَابَهُم <span class=end>٢٦</span>"}]}}